    {
        "content": "<p>Ah! noncomm_ring is <code>simp only [...]</code> then <code>abel1</code> (in this case), and the <code>simp only</code> isn't seeing through the <code>z</code> but the <code>abel1</code> is. And then the second <code>simp only</code> can go further, and close the goal. And <code>noncomm_ring [z]</code> makes it work in context.</p>",
        "id": 472994841,
        "sender_full_name": "Bhavik Mehta",
        "timestamp": 1727398385
    },
    {
